    Implementation of the monitoring endpoints for CTS CRUDL operations (except query and delete) for specific token type.
    This endpoint should not be used for query(list) and delete operations on the CTS. This is because the token type cannot be determined for these operations. For query and delete operations use the CtsCRUDOperationsEntryImpl.
